Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥 你为何把洛阳让给孙坚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自己却要追杀董卓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.57,0:00:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说是一片废墟重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.57,0:00:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还是一个天子重要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那当然是天子了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}洛阳已是一片废墟 无用之物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天子才是宝中之宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果我们能劫回圣驾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绝对是汉廷头功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.89,0:00:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从此之后各镇诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都要对我们刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}朝廷至少也得赦封我为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}西凉刺史或者是冀州太守
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由此我们就可以奠定大业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.07,0:00:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.53,0:00:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过大哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们明明只有四千兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您为何对孙坚说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们有万余精骑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:00:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果我不这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:00:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他能把他的三千战骑交给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥 此行我们是孤军追杀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓虽然败了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但他的西凉败军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}仍然不下于数万啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乘胜进军不在兵寡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}溃逃之师无惧其多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可吕布在他身边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此人可是骁勇无比呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你估计自己战得过吕布吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如论单打独斗 我非他之敌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.84,0:01:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但如论排兵布阵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他不是我的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说对了 吕布虽然骁勇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.64,0:01:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}却是一介匹夫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绝对成不了气候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}西凉军虽多也是强弩之末
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我军虽少却是乘胜追击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.59,0:01:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}两者一盛一衰 胜负立判
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}近敌之后你无需力战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要多布疑兵 虚张声势
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让西凉军魂飞胆丧即可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.87,0:01:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而交战之时你也不要去战吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:02:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更不用去取董卓的首级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.44,0:02:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只要你不顾一切地冲上去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}给我劫回天子即可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}驾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天子啊 老臣的命苦哇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣是天底下命最苦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}苦得就像是车轮底下的野草
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我苦得就像是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}石头缝里的黄连哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣为了救助大汉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不惜抛家舍业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从西凉来到了朝廷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}六年多来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣是吃不好睡不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}呕心沥血 我是如履薄冰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣的一片忠心换来了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}换来了是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}满朝的公卿大臣对老臣的恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}换来了中原诸侯对老臣的怒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}换来了数不清的明枪暗箭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阴谋诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天下的人恨不得剥老臣的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}食老臣的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣被他们逼得是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}步步走在刀刃上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣是天底下命最苦的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说是不是 天子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家可是跟你掏心窝子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是老臣唯一的一个亲人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是老臣把你摆在这个帝位上的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然我能把你摆上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想扒拉下来你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就扒拉下来你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣对你是一片忠心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你也要忠心于老臣哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说是不是 你明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明白没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父 贼军追上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不必惊慌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已命李郭二将断后了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先啊 小心护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小姐无忧 吕布在此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小姐记着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这世上有我就有你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉啊 貂蝉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉小姐 貂蝉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快 貂蝉 快把老爷扶过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多谢将军救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是我最敬仰的图腾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凤凰涅槃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爷 您慢点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好孩子 你安然无恙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我没事 好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你披的这是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是 是凤凰涅槃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}长乐宫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}汉宫生大火 长乐变长祸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}瞎说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 虽说贼兵都跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是我们得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也只是一座空城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这皇宫好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要是早生十年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就可以到这里来玩玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}权儿 策儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董贼乱京 祸满天下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}四百年的大汉王朝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一夜间竟变成了一片灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是大汉的命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是大汉天子的传国玉玺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}传国玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将年幼的时候就听家父说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这传国玉玺上锲着八个字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}受命于天 既寿永昌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}春秋年间 卞和采玉进入荆山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看见一只金凤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}落在一块大青石上鸣叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}卞和便剖开青石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}采得一块绝世美玉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}便把它献给了楚王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}秦灭六国后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这块玉就落入了秦皇的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}丞相李斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}亲自篆刻了这八个字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}秦皇就把它列为传国玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欲传百世 千世 万世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公 你看 就是它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}程普叔叔说得非常对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 权儿也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那你说说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}秦皇嬴政得到这块传国玉玺以后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}根本就没有传千世万世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}仅仅传了两世暴秦就亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}后来由我高祖皇帝一统天下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}建立了大汉王朝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玉玺落到了高祖手里以后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又传了十五代君王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一百多年前王莽篡逆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孝元皇太后就用这块玉玺砸贼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玉玺掉在了地上崩坏了一角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}后来匠人们就用黄金镶补了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二弟 你是怎么知道那么多的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今日上天把玉玺授命于主公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}足见主公有九五之尊哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恭喜爹可以称帝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是谁知道这东西是福是祸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥 难道你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}秦皇想用它传千世 万世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可仅仅传了两世暴秦就亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}程普
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}传令各部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}立刻收拾行装
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天一早随我返回江东
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁盟主率领诸侯大军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快要进城来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们到底是来了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣刘备拜祭列位先皇天灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董贼祸乱天下 玷污宫廷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}焚毁宗庙 亵渎皇纲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣身为帝胄后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}进不能剿贼建功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}退不能保境安民
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}惭愧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}愧对列位先祖先皇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥啊 这说两句就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁知道先帝爷他听得见听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘备今日在先祖先皇面前立誓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此生此世臣定要剿灭叛贼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}戡平四海 光复宗庙 中兴皇室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玄德老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我且问你 袁绍何在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我听说在嘉德殿上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为孙坚置酒庆功呢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你可愿意随我去见他一面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 我与你去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙将军 请
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德兄班师回朝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大胜而归吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}救回圣驾了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我没有得胜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我大败而归而且败得极惨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我星夜率兵追杀董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不料在荥阳遭遇吕布的伏击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}部骑伤亡过半
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果不是曹洪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把他的战马让给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此刻我已经命丧吕布戟下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德孤军追杀 勇冠三军
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽败犹荣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也有一句痛彻心扉的话想说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说 说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}匹夫竖子 不相与谋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹操 你这话什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍 袁盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我等会盟以来至少有三次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以把董卓扑灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是都被你们生生给错过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第一次就是我等会盟之初
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我建议趁董卓无防
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}兵分五路攻取洛阳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是你们不听
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是董卓刚刚出关的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我建议出骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}攻袭董卓的后方大营
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是各路诸侯各为名利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}争权夺利 勾心斗角
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都不愿意率先出兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第三次 就是董卓西迁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我率兵追杀的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们本该派出所有的精骑骁将
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}星夜驰援于我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是你们都按兵不动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}致使我大败
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:19:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这话就是孟德兄不对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为何追杀董卓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是因为你贪功心切孤军深入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何呀 你想独自劫得天子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么样 中了董卓的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那才大败而至
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没错 我是有些轻率
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}中了董卓的伏击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是在我被伏击之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果能有上万的精骑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}继续追杀下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一定能够斩杀董卓劫回圣驾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为已经有了一次伏击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就绝不会再有第二次伏击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓伏击得逞之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必然志得意满 已成骄兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他料定我们不敢追杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}根本想不到追兵之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还会再有追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德此话深得兵法精髓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只可惜我兵败之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}实在是无力继续追杀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是我回来一看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各位诸侯居然在这儿烹羊宰牛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}饮酒作乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我曹某经此大败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经看透了列位的心机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们名为扶汉剿贼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}实际上都是在谋取自己的私利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹某深以为耻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谨此告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玄德也要走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其实在下早已经告过辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只不过内心还有报国之思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以才徘徊不定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁盟主既然问起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下正好直言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我三兄弟自会盟以来屡立战功
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}非但没有得到任何犒赏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}反而处处受到刁难
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天刘备也斗胆问一下袁氏兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们二位是想除贼扶汉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还是想借除贼之名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}趁机掠取天下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我刘备宁肯落入草莽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也羞与尔等为伍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我孙坚自入盟以来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}始终担当先锋大任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}破白马 战虎牢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是一直得不到大营的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}致使我江东子弟死伤过半
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我孙坚如何向他们的父母交代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听孙将军的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}像是也要告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}君子绝交不出恶言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我战伤发作 不能再战了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我准备明日率部返回江东
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙将军之疾恐怕不是战伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是为了那块传国玉玺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}文台兄 俗话说得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要想人不知 除非已莫为
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:22:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那块玉玺是天子的命脉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}朝廷的大宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}任何臣子都不得私自藏匿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.80,0:23:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}否则就有不臣之心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有谋国之嫌哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你既然拿到了传国玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.98,0:23:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了避免众诸侯起疑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.01,0:23:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}理应放在盟主这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}日后我也好进献给朝廷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}归还予天子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.39,0:23:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}并奏报你的护国之功
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.03,0:23:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}否则 众诸侯会说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们舍生冒死地剿贼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}贼在哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来我们自己的大营里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.34,0:23:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出了妄想篡帝的国贼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么 袁盟主暗布甲士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.22,0:23:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是想杀了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}断断不是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.29,0:24:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过我既然身为盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.00,0:24:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就必须要秉公办事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.87,0:24:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为朝廷拿回传国玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.57,0:24:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这点还请文台兄多多见谅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.94,0:24:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来人 将孙坚拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.04,0:24:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.01,0:24:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来人 在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.76,0:24:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}文台兄 别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.40,0:24:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你我还是从长计议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.00,0:24:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请袁盟主讲清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.84,0:24:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我孙坚有没有藏匿传国玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.21,0:24:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有 没有 绝对没有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.21,0:25:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我孙坚是不是妄图称帝的国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.15,0:25:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是 不是 绝对不是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.92,0:25:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.86,0:25:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那你以后
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.69,0:25:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如何对各路位诸侯解释
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.03,0:25:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就说孙将军战伤复发
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.04,0:25:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}引兵回江东养伤去了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.66,0:25:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}分崩离析
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.16,0:25:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恩断义绝
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.03,0:25:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}反目成仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.84,0:26:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此番别后不知何日才能相见
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.38,0:26:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再见时也不知你我之间
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.48,0:26:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是敌是友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.65,0:26:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今后无论发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.26,0:26:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我孙某绝不与两位英雄为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.53,0:26:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要是忠于大汉之人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.06,0:26:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}便是我刘备之友
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.13,0:26:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要叛汉助贼 不管他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.14,0:26:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都是我刘备之敌
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.04,0:26:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.68,0:26:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玄德 请问你准备往哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.81,0:26:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已得到公孙将军邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.88,0:26:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}前往平原县暂驻
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.95,0:26:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请问曹将军跟孙将军呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.19,0:26:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我准备引军前往扬州
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.72,0:26:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别图救国之道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.13,0:26:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我嘛 自然是返江东故里养伤
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.83,0:26:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伤愈后
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.27,0:27:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能保境安民了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.11,0:27:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可叹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.65,0:27:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十八路英雄豪杰
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.35,0:27:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚刚起事却又星散
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.48,0:27:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从此后汉庭祸乱无休无止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.79,0:27:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玄德此言实有不确
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.26,0:27:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恕我直言
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.53,0:27:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十八路诸侯当中
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.87,0:27:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有孙文台兄 你我堪称英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.54,0:27:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其他人物不是英雄而是枭雄
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.47,0:27:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我料要不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.41,0:27:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们之间就会拼个你死我活
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.21,0:27:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我们选择尽早离开
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.62,0:27:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是为上上之策
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.42,0:27:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘备谨此告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.53,0:27:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玄德保重
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.13,0:28:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玄德保重
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.53,0:28:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹将军 孙将军保重
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.02,0:28:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德兄 告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.62,0:28:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}文台兄留步
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.26,0:28:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下有一事相问
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.60,0:28:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如有难言之处你可以不回答
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.10,0:28:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.37,0:28:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真的得到了传国玉玺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.61,0:28:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}文台兄 恕我直言
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.41,0:28:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在我看来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.78,0:28:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此物并非福气而是祸害
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.99,0:28:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁术 袁绍皆有君王之志
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.62,0:28:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无不贪恋此物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.09,0:29:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你得到的只是一块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.43,0:29:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}却可能树敌于天下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.13,0:29:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德此话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.93,0:29:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}与我小儿孙权说的倒是十分相近
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.47,0:29:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙权
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.31,0:29:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}权儿 拜见曹伯伯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.05,0:29:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜见曹伯伯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.88,0:29:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}权儿说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.12,0:29:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}秦皇想用玉玺传百世千世
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.89,0:29:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不料仅仅二世暴秦就亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.40,0:29:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.83,0:29:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有见地
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.60,0:29:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}养儿子就应该像他一样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.21,0:29:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}策儿 权儿 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.38,0:30:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保重
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.77,0:30:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}江东孙氏满门英豪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.94,0:30:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可敬可叹更可虑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.78,0:30:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍给我送了一封密信
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.48,0:30:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}约我在三津渡截杀孙坚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.29,0:30:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夺取传国玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.49,0:30:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}事成之后许我冀州三座城池
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.46,0:30:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}并报以黄金五千两
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.76,0:30:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}战马三千匹相谢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.36,0:30:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍为何非要让我截杀孙坚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.40,0:30:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此举不是有失我荆州府的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.70,0:30:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}仁义之风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.11,0:31:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是让我刘表左右为难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.38,0:31:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.71,0:31:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍的势力比孙坚强盛很多
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.98,0:31:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他既然想夺传国玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.29,0:31:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}则说明他怀有君王大志
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.92,0:31:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公如果能助他一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.92,0:31:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么不但荆州无忧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.69,0:31:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}日后我们还可以借袁绍的势力
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.16,0:31:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相机向青州冀州一带扩展
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.93,0:31:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如此 主公的前途不敢限量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.04,0:31:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再者 孙坚素来藐视我家主公
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.97,0:31:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}江东战船也不时侵犯吾境
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.41,0:31:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将赞同与袁绍结盟攻杀孙坚
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.08,0:31:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}借袁绍之力消除荆州大患
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.88,0:31:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙坚骁勇无比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.95,0:31:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凭心而论
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.06,0:31:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你二人是孙坚的对手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.37,0:31:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公 孙坚勇虽勇
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.00,0:31:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但他有勇无谋
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.74,0:32:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下有一计
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.77,0:32:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果主公能依计行事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.98,0:32:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}定能灭掉孙坚
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.63,0:32:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吁
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.63,0:32:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲 有一人自称是袁术密使
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.94,0:32:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想要见你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.54,0:32:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此人何在
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.75,0:32:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是何人 为何要见我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.55,0:32:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下袁术帐前谋士范进
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.02,0:32:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}受袁将军所托在此专候孙将军
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.83,0:33:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何事啊 说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.63,0:33:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军请看
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.97,0:33:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}弟袁术百拜文台兄
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.94,0:33:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先前会盟时
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.81,0:33:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}弟克扣将军粮饷等事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.18,0:33:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全是奉袁绍所命
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.15,0:33:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍早有帝王之心
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.42,0:33:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}意图借会盟之机壮大实力
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.45,0:33:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}取代董卓独霸天下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.29,0:33:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在他已经密信荆州刘表
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.22,0:33:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}许以重利
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.59,0:33:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}约刘表在三津渡设伏
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.13,0:33:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}截取传国玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.23,0:33:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}文台兄千万小心哪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.97,0:33:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁公路为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.87,0:33:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把这么机密的事告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.10,0:33:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道他不是袁绍的兄弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.31,0:33:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}同姓未必同道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.44,0:33:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我家主公乃仁义之君
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.58,0:33:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍则是假仁假义
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.91,0:33:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}口蜜腹剑之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.05,0:33:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我家主公不忍见孙将军蒙难
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.98,0:33:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更不愿让袁绍祸乱天下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.46,0:34:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁术在信中
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.60,0:34:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大谈对我孙坚的敬重之情
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.23,0:34:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要与我结成生死同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.94,0:34:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}共图大业
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.27,0:34:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}两位袁氏兄弟表面亲如手足
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.54,0:34:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}内心都是尔虞我诈
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.74,0:34:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}依我看来 这两人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.98,0:34:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都是贪图我的传国玉玺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.02,0:34:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们说说我们如何应付
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.76,0:34:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.92,0:34:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}依我看袁术比袁绍更可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.06,0:34:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他连自己的堂哥都可以出卖
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.50,0:34:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.07,0:34:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我部刚受重创
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.84,0:34:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公又身负战伤
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.17,0:34:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不到万不得已的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.24,0:34:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要与刘表交兵
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.94,0:34:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们还是设法绕过三津渡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.25,0:35:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三津渡是返江东的要道
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.75,0:35:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已经命令渡船在那里等候
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.02,0:35:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果绕过三津渡
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.76,0:35:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}非但渡船在那儿白等一场
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.33,0:35:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且我们的归程
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.73,0:35:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也要延长二十多天
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.80,0:35:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}特别是各部已经断了粮
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.37,0:35:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而我们的后续粮草
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.44,0:35:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都在渡船上哪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.14,0:35:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.81,0:35:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请主公不要生气
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.88,0:35:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.81,0:35:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}万般祸事都源自玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.71,0:35:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公自从得到那方传国玉玺后
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.35,0:35:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各地诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.42,0:35:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都像恶狗一般瞪大了眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.52,0:35:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}眼下袁绍袁术贪图玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.16,0:35:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公何不抛出它来让二袁相争
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.29,0:35:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如此可保江东太平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.30,0:35:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}黄叔万万不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.43,0:35:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这传国玉玺乃是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.70,0:35:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上天授予我父亲的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.57,0:35:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岂能让给他人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.84,0:35:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要我说 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.07,0:35:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘表现在已经老迈昏聩了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.44,0:35:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绝非我敌
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.81,0:36:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要我们集中五千精兵
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.88,0:36:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由我来打先锋
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.38,0:36:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我保证在三个时辰之内
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.35,0:36:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}擒下刘表 攻克荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.79,0:36:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿啊 荆州城防坚实
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.53,0:36:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}城中又有数万兵甲
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.13,0:36:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}仓促之间你攻不下呀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.63,0:36:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}程普 黄盖
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.80,0:36:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将在
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.40,0:36:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们俩率本部人马
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.77,0:36:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在三津渡北面设下疑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.81,0:36:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.57,0:36:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙策
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.41,0:36:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孩儿在
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.94,0:36:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你率两千精兵在南面设下埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.11,0:36:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.62,0:36:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果刘表敢动兵甲
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.78,0:36:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们相机杀出
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.15,0:36:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}直取刘表首级
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.46,0:36:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲 那你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.00,0:36:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘表不是冲我来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.37,0:37:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我就带几百老弱残兵
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.04,0:37:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去会会他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.18,0:37:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘表 想取我孙坚的首级吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.31,0:37:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}文台兄别来无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.44,0:37:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘兄此行何为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.98,0:37:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}特来给你送一份薄礼
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.15,0:37:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍给我的密信
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.91,0:38:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.34,0:38:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍让你截杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.04,0:38:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你孙坚最了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.25,0:38:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我刘表将过半百 体弱多病
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.62,0:38:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胸无大志 手无长技
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.92,0:38:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只想保荆州九郡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.82,0:38:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上不负皇恩
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.30,0:38:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下不负黎民百姓罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.44,0:38:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是袁绍却让我在此设伏
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.85,0:38:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让我截杀足下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.22,0:38:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这真叫我左右为难哪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.59,0:38:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敢问刘兄
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.29,0:38:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如何决定
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.04,0:39:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我思来想去
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.81,0:39:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有率军在此布阵
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.78,0:39:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其用意是假做拦截
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.48,0:39:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遮人耳目 敷衍袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.35,0:39:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在文台兄
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.72,0:39:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可以率军冲过我的战阵
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.49,0:39:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}直奔三津渡
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.46,0:39:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.03,0:39:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要贵部的号角一响
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.23,0:39:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我荆州的军阵
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.83,0:39:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立即败退 绝不交战
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.40,0:39:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之后我可以向袁绍禀报说
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.31,0:39:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我刘表无能 拦截失败
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.24,0:39:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我荆州的兵马反而遭到了损失
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.71,0:39:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样我就既不得罪他袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.75,0:39:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不得罪你孙坚了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.99,0:39:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文台兄 这就是我的两全之策
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.76,0:39:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.29,0:39:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此话当真
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.10,0:40:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.70,0:40:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过我确实还有一个要求
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.84,0:40:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讲
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.21,0:40:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从今往后你我两家和平相处
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.45,0:40:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你江东的兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.75,0:40:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再不要侵犯我荆州的境界了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.62,0:40:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘兄
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.19,0:40:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日起我江东兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.16,0:40:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}永远不会过荆州境界半步
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.13,0:40:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此 老朽多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.00,0:40:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文台兄 你现在可以率兵冲杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.25,0:40:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杀啊
